---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'June 4, 2025';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | OpsBash"
  description="Privacy policy for opsbash.com. Learn how we use Google Analytics, Google AdSense, and how we protect your data."
  canonicalURL="https://opsbash.com/privacy-policy"
>
<main class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: #34d399;">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2" style="color: var(--fg);">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--fg3);">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-5">

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        OpsBash ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website at opsbash.com. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have. By using opsbash.com, you agree to the practices described in this policy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">We collect no tool input data</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        All tools on opsbash.com run entirely in your browser. Any input you enter, such as a cron expression, is processed locally and is never transmitted to our servers. We do not store, log, or have access to the data you enter into any tool.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Google Analytics</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        We use <strong style="color: var(--fg);">Google Analytics</strong> to collect anonymous usage data about how visitors use opsbash.com. This includes information such as pages visited, time spent on pages, general geographic region (country/city level), device type, and browser type. This data helps us understand what tools are most useful and how to improve the site.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        Google Analytics uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to collect this information. The data collected by Google Analytics is aggregated and does not personally identify you. Google may process this data on servers located outside your country.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        Google's use of analytics data is governed by the <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline" style="color: #34d399;">Google Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Google AdSense</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        opsbash.com uses <strong style="color: var(--fg);">Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements. Google AdSense uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to serve ads based on your prior visits to opsbash.com and other websites across the internet.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to you based on your visit to opsbash.com and/or other sites on the internet. You may opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline" style="color: #34d399;">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        For more information about how Google uses data when you use our site, visit <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline" style="color: #34d399;">How Google uses data from sites that use Google services</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        opsbash.com uses the following types of cookies:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0" style="background: var(--fg3);"></span>
          <span><strong style="color: var(--fg);">Functional cookies:</strong> We use <code class="text-xs px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono" style="background: var(--code-bg);">localStorage</code> to remember your dark/light mode preference. This data stays in your browser and is never sent to us.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0" style="background: var(--fg3);"></span>
          <span><strong style="color: var(--fg);">Analytics cookies:</strong> Google Analytics uses cookies to collect anonymous usage statistics as described above.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0" style="background: var(--fg3);"></span>
          <span><strong style="color: var(--fg);">Advertising cookies:</strong> Google AdSense uses cookies to personalise the ads you see as described above.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">We do not sell your data</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        OpsBash does not sell, rent, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to any third party for commercial purposes. The only data shared with third parties is the anonymous analytics data processed by Google Analytics and the advertising data processed by Google AdSense, both described above, and solely for the purposes of operating those services.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Opting out</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--fg2);">You have several options to limit data collection:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0" style="background: var(--fg3);"></span>
          <span><strong style="color: var(--fg);">Google Analytics opt-out:</strong> Install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline" style="color: #34d399;">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a> to prevent Google Analytics from collecting data about your visits.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0" style="background: var(--fg3);"></span>
          <span><strong style="color: var(--fg);">Personalised ads opt-out:</strong> Visit <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline" style="color: #34d399;">Google Ads Settings</a> or <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline" style="color: #34d399;">aboutads.info</a> to opt out of personalised advertising.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full mt-1.5 shrink-0" style="background: var(--fg3);"></span>
          <span><strong style="color: var(--fg);">Browser settings:</strong> You can configure your browser to block or delete cookies. Note that blocking all cookies may affect the functionality of some websites.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Third-party hosting</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        opsbash.com is hosted on third-party infrastructure (such as Netlify or Cloudflare). These platforms may automatically collect standard server logs including IP addresses, request timestamps, and user agent strings in accordance with their own privacy policies. We do not control this data and it is governed by those providers' terms.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Your rights</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data including the right to access, correct, or delete data held about you. Because OpsBash does not directly collect or store personal data beyond what third-party services (Google Analytics, Google AdSense) process anonymously, requests should be directed to those services where applicable. For any other privacy questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@opsbash.com" class="hover:underline font-mono" style="color: #34d399;">contact@opsbash.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised "last updated" date. Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3" style="color: var(--fg);">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--fg2);">
        Questions about this privacy policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@opsbash.com" class="hover:underline font-mono" style="color: #34d399;">contact@opsbash.com</a> or <a href="/contact" class="hover:underline font-medium" style="color: #34d399;">use our contact page</a>. We respond within 48 hours.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>
</Layout>
